## Customising the Header

You can set options per screen:

```jsx
<Stack.Screen
  name="Home"
  component={HomeScreen}
  options={{ title: 'My Home' }}
/>
```

Or dynamically in the component:
```jsx
useLayoutEffect(() => {
  navigation.setOptions({ title: 'Updated!' });
}, [navigation]);
```
